  startTimeLabel: 8:27PM
  messages:
  - body: Hey!! Are you free for like five minutes?
    delayAfterPrevious: 2
    buttonLabel: 
    windowPrefabToOpen: {fileID: 0}
  - body: Actually it might be ten. Or two. Depends how good my code is.
    delayAfterPrevious: 3
    buttonLabel: 
    windowPrefabToOpen: {fileID: 0}
  - body: I finally made a game prototype!
    delayAfterPrevious: 2
    buttonLabel: 
    windowPrefabToOpen: {fileID: 0}
  - body: It is still very early, but the important systems are basically working.
    delayAfterPrevious: 3
    buttonLabel: 
    windowPrefabToOpen: {fileID: 0}
  - body: Probably.
    delayAfterPrevious: 1
    buttonLabel: 
    windowPrefabToOpen: {fileID: 0}
  - body: Can you test it for me?
    delayAfterPrevious: 2
    buttonLabel: 
    windowPrefabToOpen: {fileID: 0}
  - body: 'I just need you to collect some coins and reach the exit. '
    delayAfterPrevious: 2
    buttonLabel: Game_v0.1.exe
    windowPrefabToOpen: {fileID: 3365668955944777570, guid: 70ffaaedbc6ac5b4281e8472788bf99a, type: 3}
  - body: Also ignore the file name. It says v0.1, but emotionally it is like v0.8.
    delayAfterPrevious: 2
    buttonLabel: 
    windowPrefabToOpen: {fileID: 0}
  - body: "Open that file when you are ready. You know what? I\u2019m calling you
      , we\u2019re doing this....."
    delayAfterPrevious: 2
    buttonLabel: 
    windowPrefabToOpen: {fileID: 0}
